PrecisATLANTIC GROUNDFISH COMMERCIAL FISHING LICENCE FEES REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of the commercial fishing licence fees paid in advance by eight (8) licence holders who were subsequently denied access to the Atlantic groundfish fisheries resource as a result of the Northern Cod Moratorium.
